Turning Dream into reality

We at Saathi ensure every person at their old age with the will to follow their passion or stay employed get the perfect opportunity and platform to fulfill their dreams and be independent regardless of their age.

About us

We are a platform created by a young aspiring student group to support the elderly community that is ignored by society.

handcraft

cooking

painting

jogging

We provide a platform with various opportunities based on the interest of these people like handcraft, cooking, knitting, painting, yoga, music, life advice podcasts, etc.

Mission and Vision

Mission
Our mission is to reach all the elderly people who are passionate about being independent and keeping themselves engaged in life by providing them with the opportunities they are seeking.
Vision
Our Vision is to make the ignored part of the society ; i.e the elderly sector of people , become independent and live a better standard of life.
